MTV Sports: Skateboarding featuring Andy Macdonald, THQ's latest instalment within the action sports genre, is one of the most advanced skateboarding games ever. Choose to board as one of 30 skaters both professional and fantasy-- including vert
phenomenon Andy Macdonald, and then try your best to skate into the top rankings. 10 separate game modes including Stunt, Freeskate, Lifetyle, Deathmatch and moreto keep you coming back for more!
* 40 huge and gorgeous levels: indoor and outdoor parks, buildings, streets, schools and more
* Sixty distinct tricks - groupable into literally thousands of combos
* Soundtrack featuring music from The Deftones, System of a Down, Cypress Hill, Pennywise, and others 